## 実装例

```python
def timer(func):
    def wrapper(*args, **kwargs):
        start = time.time()
        result = func(*args, **kwargs)
        print(f"{func.__name__}: {time.time() - start:.2f}秒")
        return result
    return wrapper

@timer
def slow_task():
